                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-503983950" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-503983950" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="503983950">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/shiyifei0220/">养气女史地板君</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-03-04</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">给政治哲学吐槽帝跪了。前半部分关于大学生的吐槽句句打脸，中间哲学吐槽看得文盲压力很大，后面大学吐槽略微有点cliche。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="739198760">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-739198760" class="vote-count">2</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-739198760" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="739198760">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
