            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="17877795">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">人有没有拒绝卓越或祟高的权力？换句话说，人有没有祟高的义务？</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/17877795/">(<span class="">1回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-04-19 12:40</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                人有没有拒绝卓越或祟高的权力？换句话说，人有没有祟高的义务？
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
